OL,3,CDaughter of man who escaped Gresford
OL,4,Cdisaster sings in opera to mark
OL,5,Canniversary
OL,7,FA pensioner whose father narrowly
OL,8,Fmissed being caught up in the Gresford
OL,9,Fcolliery disaster is to sing in a new
OL,10,Fopera commemorating the 90th
OL,11,Fanniversary of the tragedy.
OL,13,FIvor Owen Bellis had injured his hand
OL,14,Fwhile down the pit the night before an
OL,15,Fexplosion and fire killed 266 men and
OL,16,Fboys in of one of Britain's worst coal
OL,17,Fmining disasters, on September 22,
OL,18,F1934.
