OL,7,FWhen the small cut turned into a large
OL,8,Fand painful blister, the 18-year-old's
OL,9,Fmother refused to let him go to work
OL,10,Fafter seeing his hand.
OL,12,FNow, 90 years later, his daughter,
OL,13,FGillian Davies was determined to be
OL,14,Fpart of the new community opera,
OL,15,F'Gresford ` Up From Underground.'
OL,17,FShe says she might never have been
OL,18,Fborn had it not been for that "strange
OL,19,Ftwist of fate".
