OL,7,FThe 70-year-old will be a member of
OL,8,Fthe New Voices choir that will be
OL,9,Fperforming the opera with the NEW
OL,10,FSinfonia orchestra at Remembering
OL,11,FGresford, a series of events in
OL,12,FWrexham to mark the milestone
OL,13,Fanniversary of the disaster.
OL,15,F"If it wasn't for my grandmother
OL,16,Finsisting he stay at home, dad might
OL,17,Fhave been among those killed," Gillian
OL,18,Fsaid.
