OL,7,FGillian, a keen amateur soprano who
OL,8,Fbelongs to four choirs, felt compelled
OL,9,Fto join the NEW Voices choir which
OL,10,Fincludes 120 singers from across North
OL,11,FWales.
OL,13,FSome rehearsal sessions have taken
OL,14,Fplace at All Saints Church in
OL,15,FGresford, where a memorial is situated
OL,16,Fin St Catherine's Chapel. It includes
OL,17,Fa mural painted in 1994 by artist
OL,18,FDenise Bates, a book of remembrance
OL,19,Fdetailing the names of all those who
OL,20,Fdied, and a miner's lantern.
