OL,7,FGillian said: "I love singing and I
OL,8,Fhave joined in previous NEW Voices
OL,9,Fconcerts but when I heard about the
OL,10,Fsubject of this latest work I knew I
OL,11,Fhad to be a part of it.
OL,13,F"The story of the disaster has played
OL,14,Fsuch a major part in mine and my
OL,15,Fsister's life that I signed up
OL,16,Fimmediately. After all if it had not
OL,17,Fbeen for that miracle of fate our
OL,18,Ffather might have been among the
OL,19,Ftragic victims and neither of us would
OL,20,Fbe here today.
