OL,7,F"Jon and Rob are such wonderful
OL,8,Fmusicians and have done a brilliant
OL,9,Fjob making sure this performance will
OL,10,Freflect the true spirit of the
OL,11,FGresford community, and all the
OL,12,Fsurrounding towns and villages which
OL,13,Fhad their hearts ripped open by this
OL,14,Fdisaster."
OL,16,FWrexham brothers Jonathan and Robert
OL,17,FGuy, the founders of the New Sinfonia
OL,18,Forchestra, have worked with the
OL,19,FWrexham Miners' Project to organise
OL,20,Fthe local commemorations, with support
OL,21,Ffrom the Arts Council of Wales.
