OL,7,FJonathan has written the music for the
OL,8,Fopera while Robert will conduct the
OL,9,Forchestra. Poet Grahame Davies, who
OL,10,Fhails from Coedpoeth, has written the
OL,11,Fwords.
OL,13,FThe commemorations culminate with
OL,14,Fthree performances of the new opera.
OL,15,FThe first of them will be at St Giles
OL,16,FChurch in Wrexham will be for schools
OL,17,Fonly, on the afternoon of Friday, 20
OL,18,FSeptember.
