OL,7,FOn 21 and 22 September there are
OL,8,Fevening performances at St Giles'
OL,9,FChurch at 8pm.
OL,11,FRobert and Jon's grandfather, Jack
OL,12,FMonslow, was a fitter at the Llay Main
OL,13,Fand Bersham collieries.
OL,15,FJon said: "We have grown up hearing
OL,16,Fstories about the pits all our lives,
OL,17,Fso many of us have family members who
OL,18,Fwere miners or worked for mining
OL,19,Fcompanies. It is part of our heritage."
